'''米尔森街'''（Milsom Street）in 英格兰[[萨默塞特郡|萨默塞特郡]][[巴斯_(薩默塞特郡)|巴斯]]，由Thomas Lightholder建于1762年。这些建筑原本是大型联排别墅，但现在大多数用作商店，办公室和银行。大部分为三层楼，有双重斜坡屋顶和[[科林斯柱式|科林斯柱]]。

米尔森街2-22号，以及25-36号为II级登录建筑<ref name="nos2to22">{{cite web|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443087|title=Numbers 2 to 22|work=Images of England|publisher=English Heritage|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024201156/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443087|archive-date=2012-10-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="nos25to36">{{cite web|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443088|title=Numbers 25 to 36|work=Images of England|publisher=English Heritage|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024201217/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443088|archive-date=2012-10-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。24号的银行是由威尔逊和威尔科克斯设计，拥有其他建筑所没有的巴洛克式细节<ref name="bank">{{cite web|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=446686|title=No 24 (National Westminster Bank )|work=Images of England|publisher=English Heritage|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024201136/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=446686|archive-date=2012-10-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。 

米尔森街37至42号称为萨默塞特郡大楼（Somersetshire Buildings），已被列为I级登录建筑<ref name="nos37to42">{{cite web|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443089|title=Nos 37 & 38 Nos 39 & 40 Nos 41 & 42|work=Images of England|publisher=English Heritage|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018003118/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443089|archive-date=2012-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

八角形礼拜堂曾是循道会的教堂<ref name="octagon">{{cite web|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443091|title=Octagon Chapel|work=Images of England|publisher=English Heritage|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018003155/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443091|archive-date=2012-10-18|dead-url=yes}}</ref> ，现在是一家餐厅<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dlgarchitects.com/upload/pdf/czaUQvUAiFCgfGF1yvFry3ORIFNZ1gNDDp71tpXF.pdf|title=The Octagon, Bath|year=2009|publisher=RLG architects|accessdate=2009-07-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100326154304/http://www.dlgarchitects.com/upload/pdf/czaUQvUAiFCgfGF1yvFry3ORIFNZ1gNDDp71tpXF.pdf|archivedate=2010-03-26}}</ref>，从46号旁边进入。<ref name="nos43to47">{{cite web|url=http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443090|title=Numbers 43 to 47|work=Images of England|publisher=English Heritage|accessdate=2009-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024201255/http://www.imagesofengland.org.uk/Details/Default.aspx?id=443090|archive-date=2012-10-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

作为一条时髦的乔治风格大道，米尔森街出现在[[简·奥斯汀|简·奥斯汀]]的一些作品中，其中包括《[[诺桑觉寺|诺桑觉寺]]》和《[[劝导_(小说)|劝导]]》。 

在2010年的[[谷歌街景|谷歌街景]]最美街道奖评比中，米尔森街被评为“英国最时尚街道”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.google.com/landing/beststreetsuk/index.html |title=Google Street View Awards 2010 |accessdate=2010-03-08 |archive-date=2012-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107021555/http://www.google.com/landing/beststreetsuk/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8554388.stm |title=The Shambles, York, named Britain's 'most picturesque' |publisher=BBC News |date=8 March 2010 |accessdate=8 March 2010 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123225452/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/8554388.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

